The paper discusses the use of machine learning algorithms to improve optimization and signal processing algorithms, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The specific applications mentioned in the paper, such as stochastic gradient descent and compressed sensing, also suggest a potential fit for computer vision (cs.CV), information theory (cs.IT), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-categories.
